node.text:
During New York Design Week, @suiteny hosted a design conversation with @gamfratesi and GUBI to talk about the story behind the iconic Beetle Chair. See the conversation moderated by @spencercbailey here.
#gubi #gubiofficial #beetlechair #gamfratesi

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on September 14, 2021. May be an image of furniture and indoor.

node.text:
The gentle glow of the Stemlite Wall Lamp creates an atmosphere which complements both modern and traditional interiors. 
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #stemlite #billcurry

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on September 13, 2021. May be an image of furniture and living room.

node.text:
The Modern Line Sofa has a sleek, feminine and light expression that is supported with elegant slender legs, which is a true signature for Greta M. Grossman’s designs.
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #modernlinesofa #gretamgrossmann #stayottoman #spacecopenhagen #cocochair #oeostudio #stemlite #billcurry #formportfolios #epictable #gamfratesi

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on September 11, 2021. May be an image of living room.

node.text:
The Pacha Lounge Chair captured in a contemporary interior setting.

Image by @deform.space
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #pachachair #pierrepaulin

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on September 10, 2021. May be an image of furniture and indoor.

node.text:
The Multi-Lite Pendant adds character to any interior setting. Simply adjusting the shades transforms the light, enabling the light to be directed upwards, downwards or even in asymmetric beams, as seen above. 

Captured at @fredrikkarlssoninteriors's apartment
Featured in @rum_id 
Photographer @enokholsegaard 
Stylist @sofie.brunner.studio
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #multilight #louisweisdorf #homedecor #interiordesign #homeinspo #lightinginspiration

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on September 09, 2021. May be an image of table and living room.

node.text:
The Epic Coffee Table is a sculptural piece made in Italy from travertine stone. It is now available in our new travertine color, Warm Taupe - a beautifully nuanced shade of soft brown-gray, with undertones of green and a wavy striation pattern. 

#gubi #gubiofficial #epictable #gamfratesi

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on September 08, 2021. May be an image of furniture.

node.text:
Slender and sturdy. The Stemlite was inspired by the strong, organic, yet slender stems that support flower heads in nature.

#gubi #gubiofficial #stemlite #billcurry

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on September 07, 2021. May be an image of furniture and indoor.

node.text:
The Coco Chair captured in a contemporary interior setting. The inspiration of the design comes from a desire to create a simple yet elegant chair with a minimal use of materials and tools without compromising the design and character. 

Image by @elledecorationdk 
Styling by @pellahedeby 
Photo by @kristofer_johnsson 
From the home of @carolinastorm and @mattiasstorm
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #cocochair #oeostudio

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on September 06, 2021. May be an image of furniture and living room.

node.text:
Select a comfortable, low-slung seat and set yourself up for a moment of meditation. The Pacha Lounge Chair is a joyfully modernist creation which embraces both extreme comfort and effortless versatility. 

Image via @abfabgram
Lighting by @giopatocoombes
Images produced by @notoostudio
Sofa by @tacchini_italia_forniture
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #pachaloungechair #pierrepaulin

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on September 05, 2021. May be an image of furniture and indoor.

node.text:
A striking silhouette with universal appeal. With its organic form, remarkable comfort and endless configurations, The Beetle Dining Chair by @Gamfratesi possesses all attributes.

Image via @stayatport
Photo by @bubblyaquarius
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #beetlechair #gamfratesi

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on September 04, 2021. May be an image of furniture.

node.text:
Sitting in the clouds. Curvaceous, soft and low-slung, the Pacha Sofa is a joyfully modernist creation which embraces both extreme comfort and effortless versatility.
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #pachacollection #pachacomfort #pachasofa #pachaottoman #pierrepaulin #violinchair #gamfratesi

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on September 03, 2021. May be an image of furniture and indoor.

node.text:
Light, fresh and elegant. The Violin Chair by @gamfratesi has a minimalist profile that epitomizes GamFratesi’s craftsmanship, creativity, and material understanding.
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #violinchair #epictable #gamfratesi #multilite #louisweisdorf

node.text:
The GMG Chaise Longue is perfectly angled for lounging whilst preserving all the streamlined qualities of a mid-century design. 

Image by @katrin_mood for @zrobim_architects
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #gmgchaiselongue #gretamgrossman #gravitylamp #spacecopenhagen
